snippet.title: Trolls vs Vikings: Reborn - Steam Gameplay footage
snippet.description:
Trolls vs Vikings: Reborn is now available on Steam! 

To wishlist, or try the demo check out: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2940040/Trolls_vs_Vikings_Reborn/ 

The full game launches March 7th ! 

Here is a bunch of gameplay footage taken straight from the game.
Check it now at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2940040/Trolls_vs_Vikings_Reborn

For more information:
Discord: https://discord.gg/P4aTmj8 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TrollsVsVikings
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/megapopgames/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MegapopGames
